Model

Class CTS_SpaceObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • Model.CTS_SpaceObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CTS_DeepSkyObject, CTS_Planet, CTS_Star

    public abstract class CTS_SpaceObject
extends java.lang.Object
    The CTS_SpaceObject is an abstract class that provides the needed boiler plate code that is common for all entities in space.
    Author:
    Joey McMaster, Nicholas Fiegel, Matt Theisen, Jackson
